notes: No items were found with empty apply.steps. All previously 'do nothing' issues were due to unsupported step types and open.path relative path resolution.
open.path now resolves relative paths against Falcon root BEFORE creating directories, preventing open actions from silently failing or creating folders in the wrong working directory.
open.url/open.file now throw explicit errors if Start-Process fails, so you will see a real error message instead of a silent no-op.
